WEBVTT

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:32.520
became referred to
as "poor, vulnerable populations."

00:04:33.200 --> 00:04:37.016
Those are the communities
of which literature speaks about

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:40.976
as living on less than a dollar a day,

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:45.176
and they become the targets
for poverty eradication programs.

00:04:45.200 --> 00:04:46.496
And by the way,

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:49.176
they are the targets of our first

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:52.760
United Nations'
sustainable development goal.

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:58.776
Now, I'm really interested

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:01.296
that we find solutions to poverty